ography information for Lord Freud","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/637265/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/637265/answer",,,,,"29","Work and Pensions","Work and Pensions","2016-11-15","Work and Health Programme","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government how many disabled jobseekers will be able to access specialist support through the proposed Work and Health Programme.","false","Biography information for Baroness Burt of Solihull",,"Baroness Burt of Solihull","HL3190"
