"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/637334","Department for Exiting the European Union","false","2016-11-22","<p>The budget will be voted on by Parliament at the Supplementary Estimate and published in line with standard practice.</p>",,"Lord Bridges of Headley",,"2016-11-22T14:27:09.487Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/637334/answer","Biography information for Lord Bridges of Headley","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/637334/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/637334/answer",,,,,"203","Exiting the European Union","Exiting the European Union","2016-11-15","Department for Exiting the European Union: Public Expenditure","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government what will be the cost of setting up and running the Department for Exiting the European Union during the 2016–17 financial year.","false","Biography information for The Marquess of Lothian",,"The Marquess of Lothian","HL3259"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/637335","Department for Exiting the European Union","false","2016-11-29","<p>All departments are equipping themselves with the resources they need to get the best deal for the UK. The Department for Exiting the European Union now has just over 300 staff, and is growing fast. We are not in a position to give a final total for particular groups of staff as recruitment is ongoing and we will not be giving a running commentary. The Government is united in its ambition to deliver a successful withdrawal from the EU and a new relationship with Europe.</p><p> </p>",,"Lord Bridges of Headley","HL3261 ; HL3262","2016-11-29T16:01:42.653Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/637335/answer","Biography information for Lord Bridges of Headley","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/637335/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/637335/answer",,,,,"203","Exiting the European Union","Exiting the European Union","2016-11-15","Department for Exiting the European Union: Staff","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government how many civil servants are employed by the Department for Exiting the European Union; and how many more they plan to recruit.","false","Biography information for The Marquess of Lothian",,"The Marquess of Lothian","HL3260"
